@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Create a course
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/courses/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Computer Engineering",
  "code": "CPEN 312",
  "credit_hours": 4,
  "professor": "Dr. Asante",
  "color_hex": "#1A73E8"
}

### Get all courses
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/courses/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
